  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DrivingDirections</Type>
    <Text>• Driving directions from LaGuardia Airport:
Take Grand Central Parkway west to I-278 (Brooklyn-Queens Expressway) west. Exit to SR 25A and bear right onto Queens Plaza north. Continue on Queensboro Bridge, and exit onto Second Avenue. Head south, then turn right onto East 57th Street. Turn right again onto Tenth Avenue, then right again onto West 58th Street. The Husdon entrance is on the right just past Ninth Avenue.
</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>• Hudson Cafeteria - Despite its name, the hotel's restaurant offers service at long, communal tables as well as standard ones. The menu at lunch and dinner is eclectic. Al fresco service is offered on the adjoining terrace in good weather.
• Hudson Bar - This ultra-stylish hotspot, popular for people-watching, features a glass floor lit from beneath, a hand-painted ceiling mural by Italian artist Francesco Clemente, and distinctive seating.
</Text>
